    About this item

    • AI Translation Smart Glasses: GetD smart glasses are your ideal travel companion, equipped with the GetD Smart App and four translation modes: AI dialogue (with ChatGPT), multi-language, voice-to-text, and face-to-face translation. Supporting 17 languages, they ensure smooth communication across Europe, America, Asia, and Latin America, making travel easier and more enjoyable.
    • Music Glasses: GetD smart music glasses are equipped with the latest Bluetooth 5.4 technology, ensuring a stable connection and seamless support for Apple and Android AAC codecs. Each temple features dual sound outlets for enhanced stereo effects, paired with GetD's advanced audio gain technology. This combination delivers superior sound quality, making every listening experience richer and more immersive. Perfect for enjoying music on the go.
    • Fashion Sunglasses/High-Quality Materials: GetD smart glasses combine style with durability, crafted from premium materials. The polarized lenses offer excellent light transmittance and color accuracy, reducing glare while maintaining clear vision. The frame and temples feature an oil-sprayed finish, creating a stunning look under sunlight. Enhanced with a specialized coating, these glasses are highly wear-resistant and scratch-resistant, making them both fashionable and long-lasting.
    • Anti-Ultraviolet and Anti-Blue Light: GetD smart glasses feature high-quality TAC lenses with advanced coatings that are oil-resistant, wear-resistant, scratch-resistant, and drop-resistant. Designed for comprehensive eye protection, the GG13 model blocks harmful blue light and offers UV400 anti-ultraviolet protection. Whether indoors or outdoors, these glasses enhance comfort while safeguarding your vision.
    • ENC Noise Reduction Microphone and HiFi Speaker: The microphone of GetD smart glasses uses ENC noise reduction to enhance sound collection, filter out background noise, and improve call clarity, ensuring the other party hears you clearly. The built-in high-quality speakers deliver immersive stereo sound for hands-free calls or music. With high-definition audio, GetD smart glasses make every listening experience enjoyable and crystal clear.

    Product description

    AI Translation

    AI Conversation with ChatGPT in the GetD Smart APP

    For iPhone: Search "GetD" or "GetD Smart" on the App Store.

    For Android: Search for "GetD Smart APP" on the APKPure platform, or contact our store manager to obtain a download QR code for the app.

    Log in: Click the Apple or Google icon to log in with your account.

    Powerful, Premium, High-Performance Hardware Integration

    The Latest Bluetooth 5.4 Version

    ENC Noise-canceling Microphone

    Adopts the latest Bluetooth 5.4 version, fast data transmission, stable signal, and anti-interference

    AI Chip: ENC noise reduction can filter out environmental noise and significantly improve the radio effect, allowing the other party to hear it more clearly

    Integrated and ergonomic design

    GG13 adopts integrated and ergonomic design.

    Precise internal structure: independently developed and designed by GetD technical team, each high-performance chip is integrated into a PCB board

    In addition, it also uses high-quality speakers that are far superior to other products, and cleverly designs the battery at the end of the temple, achieving good weight distribution, making you more comfortable to wear and fatigue-free all day long

    360 surround sound and HIFI sound quality

    Unique design: Four sound outlets

    Dual sound outlet design: After repeated polishing by the GetD audio team, the best sound outlet position and listening effect are determined. Only 30% of the volume is needed to get the audio experience that other products require 50% volume to get

    HIFI sound quality: uses high-quality speakers with clear sound quality and full sound. The design of four sound outlets on the left and right allows you to better experience the surround sound effect and bring an immersive audio-visual experience

    Large battery and magnetic fast charging

    10 hours of music play time and 2 hours of fast charging

    Using high-quality lithium batteries with large capacity, it has more than 1,000 charging cycles, which is safe and reliable. It can play music for 10 hours under the standard test environment of 60% volume, simulating the daily use environment so that you only need to charge it once every 2 days.

    Magnetic charging: It can be fully charged in just two hours, and the standby battery life is more than 15 days.

    Magnetic charging makes GG13 more airtight (IP54), achieving waterproof in daily life.

    High-quality lenses

    Polarized, anti-blue light, anti-ultraviolet

    Polarized: GG13 uses polarized lenses to effectively reduce strong light, and the outdoor visual experience is excellent

    Anti-blue light: GG13 has an anti-blue light coating, which makes your eyes more comfortable when using electronic devices and protects your eyesight

    Anti-ultraviolet: UV400 level anti-ultraviolet effect

    In addition, GG13 also has anti-oil, anti-scratch, anti-fog and other coatings to bring you an excellent user experience

    Durability and Comfort

    TR90 Material and Precision Hinges

    TR90, a high-performance eyeglass material, is lightweight, hypoallergenic, corrosion-resistant, and heat-resistant, offering comfort and durability. Its wide range of colors combines style and resilience.

    The precision-engineered eyeglass hinges ensure smooth operation and long-lasting durability, with a flexible structure that enhances stability and prevents loosening or breakage, ideal for everyday wear.

        The Quick Registration Guide

        Merchant Video

      Smart glasses

      GetD APP provides you with a good software and hardware interaction experience

      Drink water reminder: After you set the drinking target and drinking time interval, GG13 will remind you through language or message notification. (Science shows that drinking about 1.5L of water a day is good for health and metabolism)

      Sedentary reminder: It is used to remind you to get up and move to avoid cervical spine and lumbar strain and muscle soreness caused by long-term sitting

      Health Assistant

      Data integration for easy viewing

      Sports data viewing: GetD APP integrates your exercise data, including exercise health data such as exercise steps, calorie burn, exercise distance, average number of steps, etc.

      Built-in music: The GetD app has built-in sounds from nature, such as rainy day sounds, thunder and lightning, stream sounds, frog chirping sounds, ocean waves, forest sounds, campfire sounds, and sounds to help you fall asleep quickly, as well as music suitable for meditation.

      Helps you rest and relax better.

      GetD AI

      GetD technology

      GetD smart glasses realize GetD's own AI technology algorithm through built-in chips, AI algorithms, and open interfaces.

      AI Dialogue: By docking with ChatGPT to achieve intelligent Q&A in the GetD app, you can get an intelligent conversation experience by language, manual input, or copy and paste.

      Voice-to-Text: Speech-to-text is widely used in scenarios such as conference minutes, cross-border conferences, classroom education, and cross-border travel.

      Intelligent translation

      A must-have artifact for international travel

      AI Translation: Use the GetD app to achieve accurate and fast translations, making your international travel more convenient.

      Face-to-face translation: It is convenient for you to better translate when communicating with people face-to-face.

      Supports translation in seventeen languages: English, Chinese, arabic, polish, german, russian, french, korean, dutch, portuguese, japanese, thai, ukrainian, spanish, italian, hindi, indonesian.

      Custom music

      Rich features

      Custom sound effects: You can customize the sound effects by connecting the glasses to the APP and setting the sound effects according to the style you listen to, with 6 built-in sound effects, including natural (default), rock, pop, classic, jazz, country, etc.

      The equalizer also allows you to adjust it according to different frequencies, such as increasing the bass content.

      Find glasses: Using this feature, glasses will beep so you can find it. (Bluetooth connection required)

      Broad compatibility

      Bringing you an extraordinary intelligent interactive experience

      App Compatibility: The GetD app supports

      GG13 Compatibility: The GG13 features Bluetooth 5.4, supports older Bluetooth versions, and can connect to phones, laptops, tablets, and other Bluetooth-enabled devices.

      Simple Registration and Login: iOS and Android users can quickly log in with Apple or Google accounts.

      24-Hour Customer Support: We will respond to all customer inquiries within 24 hours, ensuring your questions and concerns are resolved promptly.

      These smart sunglasses feature voice assistant activation (Siri, Google Assistant, Bixby) and wireless control for settings. Operate by pressing and holding the left or right temple for 3 seconds. Stylish, convenient, and efficient.

      Please ensure the device is fully charged before use. The recommended charging time is approximately 2 hours.
